Our mission

We believe the future economy hinges upon our ability to gamify, incubate, and harness the power of DAO, NFT, and Web3 networks.

StoicDAO is here to create a stoic-minded, free-thinking, strategic community of investors who are inspired and determined to transform the modern landscape of Web3 development.

Our revolutionnary fund

StoicFund

Imagine an impact-focused and like-minded group of Web3 enthusiasts all leveraging their collective knowledge, experience, and research to invest in the future of Web3 development.

What is it?

StoicDAO holders will be able to joined together where they, alongside seasoned traders, will present, analyze and eventually vote (through our proprietary voting dApp) on potential trades/investments.

If the community votes on selling a profitable trade, 90% of the profits are then distributed to NFT holders which can be withdrawn at anytime via our dApp.

Note

Our smart contracts were designed in a way that allows for true decentralization and autonomy by auto executing trades based on successful proposals.

How does it work

Incubator

âStrong minds discuss ideas, average minds discuss events, weak minds discuss peopleâ - Socrates.

1. What is it?
The StoicDAO Incubator is an exclusive, members-only initiative that allows StoicDAO NFT holders the opportunity to submit proposals for their own NFT or Defi project.
2. How does voting work?
Once a month, DAO members will vote on which project should receive a StoicDAO investment. The investment will fund technical development of the project (smart contract, dApps, etc.) and an initial liquidity investment for Defi projects.
3. Reserve
In return, the DAO will reserve a pre-determined percentage of the project's supply, which will then be vested.
